default&#xa0;default2.7
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPassenger defaultTransport defaultIsolatiodefaultn for the Youngdefault - defaultYoung people travel
default a shorter total distance and make fewer journeys than they used to but must now make longer journeys to reach their most frequent destinations. They make most of their journeys by car but, in common with older people, they use cars less and travel by bus 
defaultmore than people in the middle age groups
