defaultThere are various Taxi Voucher Schemes in place across a few 
defaultplaces
default in 
defaultEngland, most notably in London but also in Surrey, Cheshire, Brighton and Hove for example. Outside London these vouchers amount to around £70 per year on the basis that users give up their National Bus Pass in exchange.
